These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: green, white, pink, amber, turquise
City: colone, miami, venice, san-francisco, london
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is in the middle##1
3. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
4. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
5. the person who likes green is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person traveling to venice##2
6. the person who likes turquise is in the middle##1
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
8. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Color          | white | green | turquise | amber | pink |
| City   | venice  | london      | san-francisco   | colone     | miami    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
There are 5 different nationalities: american, colombian, polish, german, indian
The people have 5 different hobbies: skydiving, singing, cooking, board-games, woodworking
1. the american is in an even position##4
2. the american is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the indian is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the polish and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the american##1
7. the polish is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Nationality   | polish     | german       | indian    | american | colombian   |
| Hobby      | singing | skydiving | board-games | woodworking      | cooking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different nationalities: indian, mexican, dutch, nigerian, malaysian
City: hannover, colone, paris, edinburgh, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the indian##1
2. the person traveling to colone is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the mexican is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
5. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
7. the dutch is on the right of the indian##1
8. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Nationality         | indian | dutch | mexican | nigerian    | malaysian |
| City   | edinburgh     | hannover        | paris      | colone | san-francisco      |

