.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: subway, boat, snowmobile, bike, motorbike
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, sunflower, daisy, dahlia, aconite
1. the person driving the snowmobile is in the middle##1
2. the person who growstulip is in an even position##4
3. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is the person who growssunflower##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
6. the person driving the boat is between the person who growsdaisy and the person driving the motorbike##2
7. the person who growsaconite is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Transport         | subway      | bike | snowmobile | boat   | motorbike  |
| Flower   | dahlia | aconite    | daisy        | tulip | sunflower |

