.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
City: liverpool, colone, san-francisco, venice, boston
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: funk, punk, indie, soul, hip-hop
1. the person traveling to liverpool is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the fan of soul##1
7. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| City      | boston      | colone | liverpool   | venice  | san-francisco  |
| Music-Genre   | indie | soul | funk | punk | hip-hop |

