.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, swimming, baseball, surfing, volleyball
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, rose, balloon-flower, azalea, aconite
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsrose is between the person who growsaconite and the person who's sport is baseball##2
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an even position##4
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
8. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Sport   | swimming        | skiing                | surfing  | baseball  | volleyball            |
| Flower        | iris | aconite | rose | balloon-flower | azalea |

