.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
There 5 different types of food: pomegranate, cranberrymelon, tomato, artichoke, cranberry
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, rowing, sailing, badminton, soccer
1. the person eating artichoke is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
3. the person eating cranberrymelon is in the middle##1
4. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
8. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Food   | cranberry       | tomato   | cranberrymelon    | artichoke    | pomegranate |
| Sport        | sailing | swimming | rowing | soccer | badminton     |

