.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-8::.
5 different games are played: bridge, domino, billiard, scrabble, backgammon
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, bellflower, marigold, balloon-flower, amaryllis
1. the person who growsmarigold is the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
5. the person who growsiris is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who growsamaryllis##2
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4    |    5    |
| Game      | billiard  | bridge       | domino      | scrabble  | backgammon   |
| Flower   | amaryllis | iris | balloon-flower | bellflower | marigold |

