.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
There 5 different types of food: pumpkin, watermelon, pineapple, potato, lemon
House: craftsman, palace, farmhouse, gothic-revival, townhouse
1. the craftsman house is in an even position##4
2. the person eating potato is the gothic-revival house##1
3. the gothic-revival house is the person eating potato##1
4. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
5. the person eating watermelon is the craftsman house##1
6. the person eating pineapple is between the person eating watermelon and the person eating pumpkin##2
7. the townhouse house is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
8. the palace house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Food   | lemon | watermelon | pineapple     | pumpkin | potato |
| House           | palace | craftsman     | farmhouse | townhouse    | gothic-revival      |

