3. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
7. the person who's birthday is in november is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Birthday     | october | september | november | july | january |
| City   | prague | nizza | san-francisco    | hannover    | miami  |

