.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, blend, montecristo, oliveros, dunhill
There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, thai, indian, colombian
1. the egyptian is on the left of the thai##1
2. the colombian is the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the colombian is in the middle##1
4. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
5. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the british is between the colombian and the blend-smoker##2
7. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
8. the egyptian is on the far left##1
9. the colombian is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Cigar        | oliveros | dunhill | aristoff  | montecristo | blend     |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | thai     | colombian | british      | indian |

