1. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
3. the siglo-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in june is between the oliveros-smoker and the person who's birthday is in january##2
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
8. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Birthday      | july       | january | june | august   | october   |
| Cigar   | siglo | game | davidoff  | oliveros | old-henry |

