.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: singing, puzzles, cooking, chess, gardening
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, futuristic, palace, modern
1. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the palace house##3
3. the craftsman house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
4. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
7. the futuristic house is in an odd position##4
8. the palace house is in the middle##1
9. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Hobby   | puzzles  | cooking    | chess | singing   | gardening |
| House   | modern | gothic-revival | palace    | craftsman | futuristic |

