4. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
5. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
6. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
7. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
8. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
9. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
