.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: water-polo, weightlifting, skiing, basketball, biathlon
There 5 different types of food: banana, lime, potato, asparagus, watermelon
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person eating potato is the person eating potato##1
3. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1
4. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person eating watermelon##2
6. the person eating lime is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person eating watermelon##2
7. the person eating asparagus is in an odd position##4
8. the person eating watermelon is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Sport         | basketball | skiing | weightlifting | biathlon | water-polo     |
| Food   | asparagus    | lime   | watermelon       | potato | banana |

