.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting-climbing, puzzles, baking, collecting, writing
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, august, july, february, november
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in february##2
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is in the middle##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's hobby is collecting-climbing##1
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Hobby   | collecting-climbing | baking      | collecting | writing     | puzzles      |
| Birthday     | november | august | february | march | july |

 